数据上报小记录

1.通过.net工具生成解析xml包

先开启MicroSuperviseCollectionApp模块33906的服务

select mx.jzmj,mx.zyjzmj,mx.ftjzmj,t4.* 
from(select zs.zl as fdzl,zs.gyqk,zs.qlbsm as djbsm,t3.* 
from(select h.bsm as hbsm,h.bdcdyh,h.zdshiyqbsm as zdjbxxbsm,h.dytdmj,h.fttdmj,h.tdsyqssj,h.tdsyjssj,h.fwjg,h.szc,h.zcs,h.tdyt,
h.tdytmc,h.fwyt1,h.ghyt,h.fwxz,
t2.* 
from (select d.dybsm,t1.* 
from (select f.bsm,f.ywh,f.qllx,f.djlx,f.djyy,f.shbsm,f.fj,f.bdcqzh,f.qxdm,f.qszt,f.qdfs,
f.tdsyqr,f.fdcjyjg,f.dbr,f.djsj,f.djjg,
f.zxywh,f.zxsj,f.zxshbsm,f.zxyy,f.zxdbr,f.zxfj
from bdcdj.fdcq f 
where ywh='F20160923-0039613') t1
left join 
bdcdj.fdcq_dygx d on d.qlbsm=t1.bsm) t2
left join
bdcdj.h h on h.bsm=t2.dybsm) t3
left join
bdcdj.djfz_cqzs zs on zs.qlbsm=t3.bsm) t4
left join
bdcdj.djfz_dymx mx on mx.qlbsm=t4.bsm;

select sbh from bdcdj.sh;

select * from b SELECT G.YWH,G.QLBSM,COUNT(*) FROM BDCDJ.FDCQ_DYGX G 
WHERE G.YWH LIKE '%2021%-%'
 GROUP BY G.YWH,G.QLBSM HAVING COUNT(*)>1;dcdj.fdcq_dygx g where ywh="%2021%-%" group by g.ywh,g.qlbsm having count(*)>1;


 SELECT * FROM BDCDJ.FDCQ_DYGX G WHERE G.YWH='20190412-0000845';
 select * from bdcdjb.fdcq2 where ywh='20190412-0000845';
